body:
Hello everyone!
I just wanted to announce that the first video that I have created on the "new' Avicus (so to say) has just been released!
This was a game of nebula on Rendezvous 3 with ipp!

Please make sure to like and subscribe!

Enjoy the video!

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DRdzeBp0DR0
